Package: europopgridviewer
Title: Shiny app to view eurostat population grids
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Wild", , "mwild@worldbank.org", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Displays eurostat population grids and allows for pdf map download, the package is based on shiny
    giscoR and mapdeck, currently only 10km and 5km grids are included.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
